main_text: 🥘 ARRÒS SEC DE SÍPIA I ESCAMARLANS 🦞⠀🚦 Fàcil⏲ 30 minuts👥 2 racions1. Daurem una sípia tallada a daus petits en una paella o cassola amb un raig d'oli i ho apartem.2. Sofregim un parell d'alls picats després afegim el mig pebrot verd italià i deixem sofregir. Quan hagi perdut la consistència afegim el tomàquet cuit pelat i picat i hi podem posar una mica de sucre morè.3. Quan hagi perdut tota l'aigua afegim un raig de conyac i desglacem. Afegim una mica de pebre vermell 3 o 4 cullerades de polpa de nyora i la cullerada grossa ceba negra sofregida. Podem afegir la melsa de la sípia i el suc dels caps dels escamarlans.4. Nacarem els 160 grams d'arròs i hi afegim els 600 ml de brou de peix ben calent. Deixem coure durant 15 minuts primer amb el foc més viu i després a foc mitjà-baix. Rectifiquem de brou si cal deixant l'arròs ben sec i cuit al dente intentant moure els grans el mínim possible.5. Col·loquem els escamarlans pelats i deixem reposar uns 5 minuts. Acabem amb uns punts d'allioli i rematem amb una mica d'escames de sal.🥘 ARROZ SECO DE SEPIA Y CIGALAS 🦞⠀🚦 Fácil⏲ 30 minutos👥 2 raciones1. Doramos una sepia cortada en dados pequeños en una sartén o cazuela con un chorrito de aceite y lo apartamos.2. Sofreímos un par de ajos picados después añadimos el medio pimiento verde italiano y dejamos sofreír. Cuando haya perdido la consistencia añadimos el tomate cocido pelado y picado y podemos poner un poco de azúcar moreno.3. Cuando haya perdido toda el agua añadimos un chorro de coñac y desglasamos. Añadimos un poco de pimentón 3 o 4 cucharadas de pulpa de ñora y la cucharada grande cebolla negra sofrita.4. Nacaramos los 160 gramos de arroz y añadimos los 600 ml de caldo de pescado bien caliente. Dejamos cocer durante 15 minutos primero con el fuego más vivo y después a fuego medio-bajo. Rectificamos de caldo si es necesario dejándolo hasta que quede al dente y bien seco intentando mover el arroz lo menos posible.5. Colocamos las cigalas peladas y dejamos reposar unos 5 minutos. Acabamos con unos puntos de alioli y rematamos con un poco de escamas de sal.

main_text: Japanese-Peruvian Cuisine at Kepong❤️‍🔥 @sushimastronikkeiGot to visit @sushimastronikkei months & I love their cozy interior and delicious cuisines!🥰 Located at Kepong Sushi Nikkei Mastro serves mouth-watering Japanese-Peruvian dishes that’ll leave you craving for more🤩 Here’s what we had:🥭 Nikkei Salmon Mango RM58 🌟🌟🌟Served w/ mango ocean fjord trout ikura shoyu zuke. The salmon cuts & mango were fresh. Love the sweet and umami combination and also the ikura that pops in your mouth💥🍚 Seafood Shirazushi RM75🌟🌟🌟Served w/ salmon hamachi hon maguro ama ebi unagi ikura tobiko barramundi red snapper malabar sushi rice - our fav item! The most GORGEOUS creation they had.❤️‍🔥🥩 Argentinian Angus Striploin RM80 🌟🌟🌟The beef was bombz!🥰 It was another fav item we had among all served with chimichurri sauce.🍙 Hamachi Uramaki RM25 🌟🌟🌟Served w/ Japanese yellowtail ginger oroshi scallions acevichada sauce - Love the complex flavours & sauce drizzled!🐟 Ikejime Surtidas RM48 🌟🌟Fish cuts [Ikejime Siakap + Ikejime Red Snapper + Ikejime Malabar] were so fresh and the quality was top notch.🥒 Edamame RM10 🌟Buttery + a perfect appetizer to start with.Other items we had:🍳Chawanmushi RM10 🌟🌟 - soft egg custard prawn ginkgo nuts mushroom🍄 Champignon Batayaki RM20 🌟🌟 - mushrooms🐟 Norwegian Halibut RM50 🌟🌟 - pan seared skinless fillet🦀️ Soft Shell Crab 🌟 - love the spicy mayo sauce🌰 Maguro Anticucho 🌟 - Borneo yellowfin tuna jalapeno salsa pine nuts🥗 Nikkei Salada🌟 - saladDrinks RM13.8 each💜 El Morado 🌟 - Butterfly pea lychee peach lemonade❤️ Sandia Jengibre 🌟 - Watermelon pandan ginger💚 Miel de Matcha 🌟 - Matcha green tea gula melaka lime🧡 Brisca Fresca 🌟🌟 - Orange pineapple peach soda8.5/10✅ Muslim-friendly📱 IG Handle: @sushimastronikkei📍 Location: Jalan Metro Perdana 6 Taman Usahawan Kepong KL [above Baskin Robbins]
comment:
{"1": {"comment_id": "hungryfoodiekl"  "comment_text": "Japanese-Peruvian Cuisine at Kepong❤️‍🔥 @sushimastronikkei

Got to visit @sushimastronikkei months & I love their cozy interior and delicious cuisines!🥰 Located at Kepong  Sushi Nikkei Mastro serves mouth-watering Japanese-Peruvian dishes that’ll leave you craving for more🤩 Here’s what we had:

🥭 Nikkei Salmon Mango RM58 🌟🌟🌟
Served w/ mango  ocean fjord trout  ikura shoyu zuke. The salmon cuts & mango were fresh. Love the sweet and umami combination  and also the ikura that pops in your mouth💥

🍚 Seafood Shirazushi RM75🌟🌟🌟
Served w/ salmon  hamachi  hon maguro  ama ebi  unagi  ikura  tobiko  barramundi  red snapper  malabar  sushi rice - our fav item! The most GORGEOUS creation they had.❤️‍🔥

🥩 Argentinian Angus Striploin RM80 🌟🌟🌟
The beef was bombz!🥰 It was another fav item we had among all  served with chimichurri sauce.

🍙 Hamachi Uramaki RM25 🌟🌟🌟
Served w/ Japanese yellowtail  ginger oroshi  scallions  acevichada sauce - Love the complex flavours & sauce drizzled!

🐟 Ikejime Surtidas RM48 🌟🌟
Fish cuts [Ikejime Siakap + Ikejime Red Snapper + Ikejime Malabar] were so fresh and the quality was top notch.

🥒 Edamame RM10 🌟
Buttery + a perfect appetizer to start with.

Other items we had:
🍳Chawanmushi RM10 🌟🌟 - soft egg custard  prawn  ginkgo nuts  mushroom
🍄 Champignon Batayaki RM20 🌟🌟 - mushrooms
🐟 Norwegian Halibut RM50 🌟🌟 - pan seared skinless fillet
🦀️ Soft Shell Crab 🌟 - love the spicy mayo sauce
🌰 Maguro Anticucho 🌟 - Borneo yellowfin tuna  jalapeno salsa  pine nuts
🥗 Nikkei Salada🌟 - salad

Drinks RM13.8 each
💜 El Morado 🌟 - Butterfly pea  lychee  peach  lemonade
❤️ Sandia Jengibre 🌟 - Watermelon  pandan  ginger
💚 Miel de Matcha 🌟 - Matcha green tea  gula melaka  lime
🧡 Brisca Fresca 🌟🌟 - Orange  pineapple  peach soda

8.5/10

main_text: 📍花蓮豐濱-船長的飛魚#利利呷花蓮🚶🏻‍♂️這間大概是我吃過最local的店了（？店裝潢真的是當地到開車直接咻過去都沒發現（好在有估狗地圖🤣🍚飛魚炒飯/120元🐟烤飛魚乾與飛魚卵香腸/180元🍲鮮魚湯/150元飛魚炒飯飯粒炒得粒粒分明調味剛好不會很鹹與魚鬆.小黃瓜.紅蘿蔔.海苔一起拌炒，靈魂精華是它的飛魚肉✨每一口都吃得出香氣呈上桌整個就是澎湃～飛魚乾烤的焦香，香腸也好吃飛魚肉原來吃起來是偏硬的肉質但魚刺不多，香腸吃得出飛魚卵口感，調味加了胡椒粉超對味！洋蔥的清爽讓你不會覺得很重口味鮮魚湯魚肉是用鬼頭刀煮的肉質鮮甜軟嫩沒有魚腥味料多實在大碗一點都不馬虎湯頭喝得出馬告的香氣很清爽來這用餐最大的特色就是有無敵海景🤩而且有路可以直接走到海邊的那種邊欣賞海景邊吃著原住民的料理真的是別有一番風味呢☺️店名：船長的飛魚地址：花蓮縣豐濱鄉港口村1鄰16號營業時間：09:00-17:00，六日至18:00（魚肉可能會視當日漁獲狀況而定）#花蓮美食#花蓮#花蓮豐濱#原住民料理#飛魚料理#飛魚炒飯#飛魚卵香腸#鬼頭刀湯#花蓮特色小吃#無敵海景#船長的飛魚#hualien#hualienfood#rice#taiwanfood#foodie#hualientravel#fengb in#indigenouscuisine#flyingfish
comment:
{"1": {"comment_id": "eator_lili"  "comment_text": "📍花蓮豐濱-船長的飛魚
#利利呷花蓮🚶🏻‍♂️
這間大概是我吃過最local的店了（？
店裝潢真的是當地到開車直接咻過去都沒發現（好在有估狗地圖🤣

🍚飛魚炒飯/120元
🐟烤飛魚乾與飛魚卵香腸/180元
🍲鮮魚湯/150元

飛魚炒飯飯粒炒得粒粒分明
調味剛好不會很鹹
與魚鬆.小黃瓜.紅蘿蔔.海苔一起拌炒，靈魂精華是它的飛魚肉✨
每一口都吃得出香氣
呈上桌整個就是澎湃～

飛魚乾烤的焦香，香腸也好吃
飛魚肉原來吃起來是偏硬的肉質
但魚刺不多，香腸吃得出飛魚卵口感，調味加了胡椒粉超對味！
洋蔥的清爽讓你不會覺得很重口味

鮮魚湯魚肉是用鬼頭刀煮的
肉質鮮甜軟嫩沒有魚腥味
料多實在大碗一點都不馬虎
湯頭喝得出馬告的香氣很清爽

來這用餐最大的特色就是有無敵海景🤩
而且有路可以直接走到海邊的那種
邊欣賞海景邊吃著原住民的料理
真的是別有一番風味呢☺️

店名：船長的飛魚
地址：花蓮縣豐濱鄉港口村1鄰16號
營業時間：09:00-17:00，六日至18:00
（魚肉可能會視當日漁獲狀況而定）

main_text: Sticky garlic butter tofu from @thefoodietakesflight I saw her video for this last night and had to make it. I used my air fryer to fry tofu for the first time. I only had firm not extra firm but after pressing it crisped up nicely. I also didn’t have any scallions so I used a little of a shallot instead which worked fine. And I used dairy butter so it’s no longer vegan. I think it’s delicious. The boy says “it’s fine” which I’ll honestly take. The second pic is three different ways to eat it in an attempt to give him options. I could see adding some vegetables to fill it out a little. And a little ginger might be nice. But it’s delicious as is. #tofu #veganish #vegan #thefoodietakesflight #rice #airfryer #dinner #homemade #homecooking #foodtheboywilleat #delicious #tasty #yum
